  "description": "A vibrant rainbow arcs over a bustling port scene. Several large, white gantry cranes dominate the middle ground, positioned above rows of colorful shipping containers stacked along a pier. The containers are various shades of red, blue, green, and yellow. The water in the foreground is a calm, dark gray, reflecting the overcast sky.  In the distance, a city skyline is visible, partially obscured by haze. The overall scene suggests a major international shipping hub.",
